<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ رَافِعِ بنِ سَلَمةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ مِنْهُ عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> بنُ موسى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَرَوَى <span class="c2">(٤)</span> عَنْهُ مُعَافى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
